231
00:07:54,224 --> 00:07:56,142
-Sim.
-Legal.

232
00:07:56,184 --> 00:07:57,644
Vejo você lá.  Tchau, tio Jason.

233
00:07:57,686 --> 00:07:58,812
-Tchau, Arabela.
-Tchau.

234
00:07:58,853 --> 00:08:00,647
